trans-unit.source: Provides an interface for developers to specify custom editing controls that are associated with a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Udostępnia interfejs dla deweloperów określić niestandardowe, które są skojarzone z formantów edycji <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> formantu.

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface enables you to associate custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls with a server control--such as a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, a user control, or a custom server control.
trans-unit.target: Interfejs IWebEditable umożliwia kojarzenie niestandardowych <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formanty z formantem serwera — takie jak <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>formantu, kontrolkę użytkownika lub formantu niestandardowego serwera.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls are contained with an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control, and this zone with its editing controls provides end users with a user interface (UI) for modifying properties, appearance, and behavior on the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Formanty znajdują się z <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontroli i tej strefy z formantami edycji oferuje użytkownikom końcowym z interfejsem użytkownika (UI), modyfikowania właściwości, wygląd i zachowanie w skojarzonych <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroli.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface includes two exposed members.
trans-unit.target: Interfejs IWebEditable zawiera dwa elementy członkowskie uwidocznione.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A> property provides a way for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to get a reference to the associated server control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A>Właściwości umożliwia <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów, aby pobrać odwołanie do formantu skojarzone serwerem.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.WebBrowsableObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method is used to create an instance of each custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> control associated with a server control, and return them as a collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>Metoda jest używana do utworzenia wystąpienia każdej niestandardowej <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantu powiązanego z formantem serwera i zwraca je jako kolekcję.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The IWebEditable interface is already implemented on the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class, although by default this implementation does not associate any custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class.
trans-unit.target: Interfejs IWebEditable został już zaimplementowany w podstawowej <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klasy, mimo że domyślnie ta implementacja nie wiąże żadnych niestandardowych <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów z <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klasy.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To associate a derived <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control with custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls, you can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Aby skojarzyć pochodnego <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>formant niestandardowy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów, można zastąpić <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>— Metoda.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls associated with a server control that implements the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Zwraca kolekcję niestandardowych <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> formanty powiązane z formantu serwera, który implementuje <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable"> </xref> interfejsu.

trans-unit.source: The CreateEditorParts method enables you to create a collection of all the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls associated with your custom control, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, or user control, and return them as an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoda CreateEditorParts umożliwia tworzenie kolekcji wszystkich niestandardowych <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formanty powiązane z formantu niestandardowego <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>formant lub użytkownika, sterowania i przywróć ich jako <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control takes the collection and creates instances of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls whenever the server control enters edit mode.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>Kontroli przyjmuje kolekcji i tworzy wystąpienia wszystkich <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formanty zawsze, gdy formant serwer przechodzi trybu edycji.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Typically you implement this method in a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control by overriding its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Zwykle zaimplementować tę metodę w niestandardowej <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroli przez zastąpienie jej <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A>metody.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CreateEditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In the method, you create instances of the custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls you want to associate with your controls, add them to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> object, and then return that object.
trans-unit.target: W przypadku metody tworzenia wystąpienia niestandardowego <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów, które chcesz skojarzyć z formantów, dodaj je do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection>obiekt, a następnie wróć tego obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls is then assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Kolekcja <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów jest przypisywana do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A>Właściwość <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>strefy.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> that is added to the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls in an implementation of the CreateEditorParts method must have a value assigned to its ID property, otherwise an exception will be thrown when the collection is assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Żadnych <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>dodana do kolekcji <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów w implementacji metody CreateEditorParts musi mieć wartość przypisana do właściwości jego identyfikator, w przeciwnym razie zostanie wygenerowany wyjątek przy przypisywaniu do kolekcji <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A>Właściwości.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.EditorParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> that contains the collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls associated with a server control.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> Zawierający kolekcję niestandardowych <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> formanty powiązane z formantu serwera.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control, user control, or custom control that will be edited by <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera odwołanie do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> formantu, kontrolki użytkownika lub kontrolki niestandardowej, która będzie można edytowane przez <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrolki.

trans-unit.source: The WebBrowsableObject property provides a way for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to get a reference to the server controls they are associated with.
trans-unit.target: Zapewnia właściwości WebBrowsableObject <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów, aby pobrać odwołanie do kontrolki serwera skojarzonych z nimi.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Although the property itself is read-only, the object reference that it returns enables <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to change values in the server control.
trans-unit.target: Mimo że samej właściwości tylko do odczytu, odwołanie do obiektu, który zwraca umożliwia <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>formantów w celu zmiany wartości w formancie serwera.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: An object reference to the control associated with an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Odwołanie obiektu do formantu skojarzony z <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> formantu.
